012) </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic">Public attitudes regarding climate change</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">, available from http://www.ipsos-mori.com/researchpublications/researcharchive/2916/Public-attitudes-regarding-climate-change.aspx</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 12pt 35.45pt; text-indent:-35.45pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">Lederman, N. G. (2007) ‘Nature of science: Past, present, and future’, in Abell, S. K. and Lederman, N. G. (eds) </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic">Handbook of Research on Science Education</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">, pp. 831-879</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 12pt 35.45pt; text-indent:-35.45pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">Neal, T. and Vernon, A. (2012) </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic">Science Museum Annual Audience Profile Report 2011/12</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">, Science Museum, unpublished</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 12pt 35.45pt; text-indent:-35.45pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">Nilsson, K., Gammon, B., McCallie, E., Simonsson, Lehr, J. (2007) ‘Learning to generate dialogue: Theory, practice and evaluation’ in </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic">Museums and Social Issues</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> 2(2) pp. 167-186</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 12pt 35.45pt; text-indent:-35.45pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">Paynter, F. (2011) </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-